languages.text: "Отсутствие воли? Фиксирую высокий риск производственного брака в священных процессах Горнила. Следует утилизировать выпущенную партию единиц и остановить производство новых, а алгоритм великого ваяния подвергнуть исследованию".

"Lack of will? Registering a high probability of manufacturing failure within the Crucible's sacred processes. It is recommended to dispose of the finished batch of units and halt production of new ones. The algorithm of the great sculpting requires further examination."

traits.locale_text: The Blessed seem to be knowledgeable in many fields, and we can learn something valuable from them. Extract the data, save a few specimen and dispose of the rest. The Tech-Priests can halt the production of the new Blessed without deleting the algorithm from the great sculpting, simply suspending it in case the new individuals would be needed."

Es wird empfohlen, die fertiggestellten Einheiten zu entsorgen und die Produktion neuer Einheiten einzustellen. Der Algorithmus der großen Formgebung erfordert eine weitere Untersuchung."
